{"id":19,"parent_id":2,"book_id":2,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":19,"title":"Matthew 17","subtitle":"","short_title":"Matt.","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 17"],[".studySummary",["i","Jesus is transfigured before Peter, James, and John on the mount—Jesus heals a lunatic, tells of His coming death, and pays taxes in a miraculous manner."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.1","order":"03.03.017.2263"},["b","1"],"And after six days Jesus taketh",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Peter"],", James, and John his brother, and bringeth them up into an high mountain apart,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.2","order":"03.03.017.2264"},["b","2"],"And was",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"transfigured"],"before them: and his face did shine as the sun, and his raiment was white as the light."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.3","order":"03.03.017.2265"},["b","3"],"And, behold, there appeared unto them",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"Moses"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_3b"},"Elias"],"talking with him."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.4","order":"03.03.017.2266"},["b","4"],"Then answered Peter, and said unto Jesus, Lord, it is good for us to be here: if thou wilt, let us make here three tabernacles; one for thee, and one for Moses, and one for Elias."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.5","order":"03.03.017.2267"},["b","5"],"While he yet spake, behold, a bright",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"cloud"],"overshadowed them: and behold a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_5b"},"voice"],"out of the cloud, which said, This is my",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_5c"},"beloved"],["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_5d"},"Son"],", in whom I am well pleased; hear ye him."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.6","order":"03.03.017.2268"},["b","6"],"And when the disciples heard",["i","it,"],"they fell on their face, and were sore",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"afraid"],"."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.7","order":"03.03.017.2269"},["b","7"],"And Jesus came and touched them, and said, Arise, and be not afraid."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.8","order":"03.03.017.2270"},["b","8"],"And when they had lifted up their eyes, they saw no man, save Jesus only."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.9","order":"03.03.017.2271"},["b","9"],"And as they came down from the mountain, Jesus charged them, saying, Tell the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"vision"],"to no",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"man"],", until the Son of man be risen again from the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"dead"],"."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.10","order":"03.03.017.2272"},["b","10"],"And his disciples asked him, saying, Why then say the scribes that Elias must first come?"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.11","order":"03.03.017.2273"},["b","11"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"And"],"Jesus answered and said unto them, Elias truly shall first come, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_11b"},"restore"],"all things."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.12","order":"03.03.017.2274"},["b","12"],"But I say unto you, That Elias is come already, and they knew him not, but have done unto him whatsoever they",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"listed"],". Likewise shall also the Son of man suffer of them."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.13","order":"03.03.017.2275"},["b","13"],"Then the disciples understood that he spake unto them of John the Baptist."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.14","order":"03.03.017.2276"},["b","14"],"¶And when they were come to the multitude, there came to him a",["i","certain"],"man, kneeling down to him, and saying,"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.15","order":"03.03.017.2277"},["b","15"],"Lord, have mercy on my son: for he is lunatic, and sore vexed: for ofttimes he",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_15a"},"falleth"],"into the fire, and oft into the water."],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.16","order":"03.03.017.2278"},["b","16"],"And I brought him to thy disciples, and they could not cure him."],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.17","order":"03.03.017.2279"},["b","17"],"Then Jesus answered and said, O",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"faithless"],"and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_17b"},"perverse"],"generation, how long shall I be with you? how long shall I suffer you? bring him hither to me."],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.18","order":"03.03.017.2280"},["b","18"],"And Jesus rebuked the devil; and he departed out of him: and the child was cured from that very hour."],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.19","order":"03.03.017.2281"},["b","19"],"Then came the disciples to Jesus apart, and said, Why could not we cast him out?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.20","order":"03.03.017.2282"},["b","20"],"And Jesus said unto them, Because of your",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_20a"},"unbelief"],": for verily I say unto you, If ye have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_20b"},"faith"],"as a grain of mustard seed, ye shall say unto this",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_20c"},"mountain"],", Remove hence to yonder place; and it shall remove; and nothing shall be",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_20d"},"impossible"],"unto you."],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.21","order":"03.03.017.2283"},["b","21"],"Howbeit this",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_21a"},"kind"],"goeth not out but by prayer and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_21b"},"fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"22","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.22","order":"03.03.017.2284"},["b","22"],"¶And while they abode in Galilee, Jesus said unto them, The Son of man shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_22a"},"betrayed"],"into the hands of men:"],["div",{"id":"23","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.23","order":"03.03.017.2285"},["b","23"],"And they shall kill him, and the third day he shall be",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_23a"},"raised"],"again. And they were exceeding sorry."],["div",{"id":"24","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.24","order":"03.03.017.2286"},["b","24"],"¶And when they were come to Capernaum, they that received tribute",["i","money"],"came to Peter, and said, Doth not your master pay",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_24a"},"tribute"],"?"],["div",{"id":"25","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.25","order":"03.03.017.2287"},["b","25"],"He saith, Yes. And when he was come into the house, Jesus",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_25a"},"prevented him"],", saying, What thinkest thou, Simon? of whom do the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_25b"},"kings"],"of the earth take custom or tribute? of their own children, or of strangers?"],["div",{"id":"26","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.26","order":"03.03.017.2288"},["b","26"],"Peter saith unto him, Of strangers. Jesus saith unto him, Then are the children free."],["div",{"id":"27","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.27","order":"03.03.017.2289"},["b","27"],"Notwithstanding, lest we should offend them, go thou to the sea, and cast an hook, and take up the fish that first cometh up; and when thou hast opened his mouth, thou shalt find a piece of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_27a"},"money"],": that take, and",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_27b"},"give"],"unto them for me and thee."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.1a","order":"03.03.017.2290"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/128.20"},"D&C 128:20"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.2a","order":"03.03.017.2292"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/9.2.2-13"},"Mark 9:2 (2–13)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/9.29.28-36"},"Luke 9:29 (28–36)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/john/1.14"},"John 1:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/2-pet/1.16.16-19"},"2 Pet. 1:16 (16–19)"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-glory-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Glory of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/transfiguration"},"Transfiguration"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.3a","order":"03.03.017.2294"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/63.21"},"D&C 63:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.11"},"110:11"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/priesthood-keys-of"},"TG Priesthood, Keys of"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/translated-beings"},"Translated Beings"],"."],["div",{"id":"3b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.3b","order":"03.03.017.2296"},["b","3b"],["span.small","IE"],"Elijah.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/17.1"},"1 Kgs. 17:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/luke/4.25"},"Luke 4:25"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.13.13-16"},"D&C 110:13 (13–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.5a","order":"03.03.017.2298"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/24.15"},"Ex. 24:15"],"."],["div",{"id":"5b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.5b","order":"03.03.017.2300"},["b","5b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-body-of-corporeal-nature"},"TG God, Body of, Corporeal Nature"],"."],["div",{"id":"5c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.5c","order":"03.03.017.2302"},["b","5c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/matt/3.17"},"Matt. 3:17"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/3-ne/11.7"},"3 Ne. 11:7"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/js-h/1.17"},"JS—H 1:17"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/witness-of-the-father"},"TG Witness of the Father"],"."],["div",{"id":"5d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.5d","order":"03.03.017.2304"},["b","5d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-2"},"TG God"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/godhead"},"Godhead"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-the-father-elohim"},"God the Father, Elohim"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-divine-sonship"},"Jesus Christ, Divine Sonship"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.6a","order":"03.03.017.2306"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/3.6"},"Ex. 3:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/5.5"},"Deut. 5:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.9a","order":"03.03.017.2308"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/vision"},"TG Vision"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.9b","order":"03.03.017.2310"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/mark/9.9.9-13"},"Mark 9:9 (9–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.9c","order":"03.03.017.2312"},["b","9c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/death"},"TG Death"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.11a","order":"03.03.017.2314"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/jst/jst-matt/17.10-14"},["span.small","JST"],"Matt. 17:10–14 (Appendix)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.11b","order":"03.03.017.2316"},["b","11b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/27.6"},"D&C 27:6"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/77.14"},"77:14"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/110.13-16"},"110:13–16"],".",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/dispensations"},"TG Dispensations"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/restoration-of-the-gospel"},"Restoration of the Gospel"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.12a","order":"03.03.017.2318"},["b","12a"],["span.small","GR"],"desired."],["div",{"id":"15a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.15a","order":"03.03.017.2320"},["b","15a"],["span.small","GR"],"throws himself."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.17a","order":"03.03.017.2322"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/unbelief"},"TG Unbelief"],"."],["div",{"id":"17b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.17b","order":"03.03.017.2324"},["b","17b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/32.5"},"Deut. 32:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"20a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.20a","order":"03.03.017.2326"},["b","20a"],["span.small","GR"],"little faith.",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/doubt"},"TG Doubt"],"."],["div",{"id":"20b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.20b","order":"03.03.017.2328"},["b","20b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/faith"},"TG Faith"],"."],["div",{"id":"20c","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.20c","order":"03.03.017.2330"},["b","20c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/ether/12.30"},"Ether 12:30"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/7.13"},"Moses 7:13"],"."],["div",{"id":"20d","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.20d","order":"03.03.017.2332"},["b","20d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/god-power-of"},"TG God, Power of"],"."],["div",{"id":"21a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.21a","order":"03.03.017.2334"},["b","21a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.67.65-73"},"D&C 84:67 (65–73)"],"."],["div",{"id":"21b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.21b","order":"03.03.017.2336"},["b","21b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/fast-fasting"},"TG Fast, Fasting"],"."],["div",{"id":"22a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.22a","order":"03.03.017.2338"},["b","22a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-betrayal-of"},"TG Jesus Christ, Betrayal of"],"."],["div",{"id":"23a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.23a","order":"03.03.017.2340"},["b","23a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/jesus-christ-resurrection"},"TG Jesus Christ, Resurrection"],"."],["div",{"id":"24a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.24a","order":"03.03.017.2342"},["b","24a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/58.21.21-22"},"D&C 58:21 (21–22)"],"."],["div",{"id":"25a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.25a","order":"03.03.017.2344"},["b","25a"],["span.small","GR"],"spoke to him first."],["div",{"id":"25b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.25b","order":"03.03.017.2346"},["b","25b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/kings-earthly"},"TG Kings, Earthly"],"."],["div",{"id":"27a","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.27a","order":"03.03.017.2348"},["b","27a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/30.13"},"Ex. 30:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ex/38.26"},"38:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"27b","uri":"/scriptures/nt/matt/17.27b","order":"03.03.017.2350"},["b","27b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/citizenship"},"TG Citizenship"],"."]]}
